This is a temporary method, in the future it will all be done via de app.

First you have to create the database:
install mysql: 
on opensuse: 

zypper in mysql
systemctl start mysql.service 
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bedi1982/Oficina/master/Oficina.sql
mysql -u root < Oficina.sql;

In the oficina software currently the database is hardcoded:
user: root
password: (leave empty)
